metadata.name: ORDINAL TELEPORT - BURN TO BRIDGE
metadata.description:
Ordinal Teleport is a collection of 333 tokens.

In the coming days, the holders will have the opportunity to burn the bulk of the supply and  get airdrop a unique 1/1 teleport.

Subsequently by burning your ETH token, holders will be able to obtain a Ordinal Teleport on the Ordinals protocol.

Also, each Ordinal Teleport holder will receive the NFT of his teleport from the other side on the Ethereum blockchain, will get access to all future Ordinal drops, as well as many other interesting things.

 Stay tuned.
